#. <section class="sutta" id="sn20.1"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn20.1:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 20"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 20"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn20.1:0.2"
msgid "1. Opammavagga"
msgstr "1. Similes"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn20.1:0.3"
msgid "1. Kūṭasutta"
msgstr "1. A Roof Peak"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.263"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. <span class="evam">
msgctxt "sn20.1:1.1"
msgid "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—"
msgstr "So I have heard."

#. </span>
msgctxt "sn20.1:1.2"
msgid "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn20.1:1.3"
msgid "Tatra kho bhagavā … pe … etadavoca:"
msgstr "There the Buddha … said:"

#. </p><p class="added">
msgctxt "sn20.1:1.4"
msgid "“seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kūṭāgārassa yā kāci gopānasiyo sabbā tā kūṭaṅgamā kūṭasamosaraṇā kūṭasamugghātā sabbā tā samugghātaṃ gacchanti;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, the rafters of a bungalow all lean to the peak and meet at the peak, and when the peak is demolished they’re all demolished too."

msgctxt "sn20.1:1.5"
msgid "evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci akusalā dhammā sabbe te avijjāmūlakā avijjāsamosaraṇā avijjāsamugghātā, sabbe te samugghātaṃ gacchanti."
msgstr "In the same way any unskillful qualities are rooted in ignorance and meet in ignorance, and when ignorance is demolished they’re all demolished too."

msgctxt "sn20.1:1.6"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "sn20.1:1.7"
msgid "‘appamattā viharissāmā’ti."
msgstr "‘We will stay diligent.’"

msgctxt "sn20.1:1.8"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr "That’s how you should train.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn20.1:1.9"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
